Millwall beat Charlton 2-1 in the Championship on Good Friday . 
  Alou Diarra gave the Addicks the lead in the second half . 
  Magaye Gueye equalised for the hosts in the 87th minute . 
  Charlton defender Chris Solly was sent off for handball in the box . 
  Jos Hooiveld scored a late winner for Millwall at The Den . 
 